        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "無色曰夷。 言一無采色，不可得視而見之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "無聲曰希。 言一無音聲，不可得聽而聞之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "無形曰微。 言一無形體，不可摶持而得之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "三者，謂夷、希、微也。 不可致詰者，夫無色、無聲、無形，口不能言，書不能傳，當受之以靜，求之以神，不可問詰而得之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "混，合也。 故合於三名之為一。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言一在天上，不皦。 皦，光明。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言一在天下，不昧。 昧，有所闇冥。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "繩繩者，動行無窮級也。 不可名者，非一色也，不可以青黃白黑別，非一聲也，不可以宮商角徵羽聽，非一形也，不可以長短大小度之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "物，質也。 復當歸之於無質。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言一無形狀，而能為萬物作形狀也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "一無物質，而為萬物設形象也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "一忽忽恍恍者，若存若亡，不可見之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "一無端末，不可預待也。除情去欲，一自歸之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 13,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言一無影跡，不可得而看。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 14,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人執守古道，生一以御物，知今當有一也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-16",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 15,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人能知上古本始有一，是謂知道綱紀也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
